        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Solar Inverter Charger&amp;quot; by the Renewable Energy Department, Government of Haryana, aims to promote sustainable energy practices, reduce the dependency on grid electricity, and provide financial support for the installation of solar inverter chargers in domestic households. This initiative targets families with existing inverters who have not yet adopted solar technology, thereby enabling energy-efficient solutions and reducing carbon footprint.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - **For 320-watt Solar Inverter Charger System:** A subsidy of ₹6,000/- is provided.  - **For 640-watt Solar Inverter Charger System:** A subsidy of ₹10,000/- is provided.\n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "\n  - The applicant should not have installed a Solar Inverter Charger in the past 5 years under the Department Scheme.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The \"Solar Inverter Charger\" by the Renewable Energy Department, Government of Haryana, aims to promote the use of renewable energy and reduce electricity dependence by providing a subsidy of ₹6,000/- or ₹10,000/- for solar inverter charger systems to eligible households.",
